### Customer Registry API - HTTP Request Examples
### Compatível com a extensão "REST Client" do VS Code e com o cliente HTTP do JetBrains.
### Ajuste @base_url conforme o ambiente.

@base_url = http://localhost:8080
@customer_id = 52f2b43e-8123-4b38-8284-dc66f2ca7748

### ===================== HEALTH =====================

### Liveness — processo vivo (200 sempre que o binário estiver rodando)
GET {{base_url}}/healthz

### Readiness — 200 se o DB respondeu ao ping, 503 caso contrário
GET {{base_url}}/readyz

### ===================== SWAGGER =====================

### Abrir a UI do Swagger no navegador
GET {{base_url}}/swagger/index.html

### ===================== CREATE CUSTOMERS =====================

### Criar cliente 1 - Risco BAIXO
POST {{base_url}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "DOC-00001",
  "name": "João Silva",
  "score": 850,
  "risk_level": "LOW",
  "income_range": "5000-8000",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Criar cliente 2 - Risco MÉDIO
POST {{base_url}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "DOC-00002",
  "name": "Maria Santos",
  "score": 650,
  "risk_level": "MEDIUM",
  "income_range": "3000-5000",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Criar cliente 3 - Risco ALTO
POST {{base_url}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "DOC-00003",
  "name": "Pedro Costa",
  "score": 400,
  "risk_level": "HIGH",
  "income_range": "1000-3000",
  "status": "UNDER_REVIEW"
}

### Criar cliente 4 - Score muito alto
POST {{base_url}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "DOC-00004",
  "name": "Ana Oliveira",
  "score": 950,
  "risk_level": "LOW",
  "income_range": "8000-10000",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Criar cliente 5 - Inativo
POST {{base_url}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "DOC-00005",
  "name": "Carlos Mendes",
  "score": 500,
  "risk_level": "MEDIUM",
  "income_range": "2000-4000",
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

### ===================== LIST CUSTOMERS =====================

### Listar todos os clientes (default: limit=20, offset=0)
GET {{base_url}}/customers

### Listar clientes com limit=2 (primeira página)
GET {{base_url}}/customers?limit=2

### Listar clientes com limit=2 e offset=2 (segunda página)
GET {{base_url}}/customers?limit=2&offset=2

### Listar clientes com limit=10 e offset=0
GET {{base_url}}/customers?limit=10&offset=0

### ===================== GET BY ID =====================

### Buscar cliente por ID (substitua @customer_id no topo pelo UUID retornado na criação)
GET {{base_url}}/customers/{{customer_id}}

### ===================== GET BY DOCUMENT =====================

### Buscar cliente por documento - DOC-00001
GET {{base_url}}/customers/document/DOC-00001

### Buscar cliente por documento - DOC-00002
GET {{base_url}}/customers/document/DOC-00002

### Buscar cliente por documento - DOC-00003
GET {{base_url}}/customers/document/DOC-00003

### ===================== UPDATE STATUS =====================

### Atualizar status para ACTIVE
PATCH {{base_url}}/customers/{{customer_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Atualizar status para INACTIVE
PATCH {{base_url}}/customers/{{customer_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

### Atualizar status para UNDER_REVIEW
PATCH {{base_url}}/customers/{{customer_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "UNDER_REVIEW"
}

### ===================== ERROR CASES =====================

### Documento duplicado (deve retornar 409)
POST {{base_url}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "DOC-00001",
  "name": "Duplicado",
  "score": 700,
  "risk_level": "LOW",
  "income_range": "5000-8000",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### JSON inválido (deve retornar 400)
POST {{base_url}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  invalid json
}

### Score fora do intervalo 0-1000 (deve retornar 400)
POST {{base_url}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "DOC-INVALID-SCORE",
  "name": "Score Inválido",
  "score": 1500,
  "risk_level": "LOW",
  "income_range": "5000-8000",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### risk_level inválido (deve retornar 400)
POST {{base_url}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "DOC-INVALID-RISK",
  "name": "Risk Inválido",
  "score": 700,
  "risk_level": "EXTREME",
  "income_range": "5000-8000",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### status inválido (deve retornar 400)
POST {{base_url}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "DOC-INVALID-STATUS",
  "name": "Status Inválido",
  "score": 700,
  "risk_level": "LOW",
  "income_range": "5000-8000",
  "status": "PENDING"
}

### Campos obrigatórios faltando (deve retornar 400)
POST {{base_url}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "",
  "name": ""
}

### Buscar cliente com ID inexistente (deve retornar 404)
GET {{base_url}}/customers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Buscar cliente com documento inexistente (deve retornar 404)
GET {{base_url}}/customers/document/INEXISTENTE

### Atualizar status de cliente com ID inexistente (deve retornar 404)
PATCH {{base_url}}/customers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}
